---
title: Creole Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Caramelised Onion Chutney & Mayo
description: This heavenly chicken coated in our Creole spice blend is full of flavour, thanks to red bell pepper, onion and garlic.
Add a medley of veggies, sweet chutney and a dollop of creamy mayo and it’s satisfaction, guaranteed!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
